Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.11,1:47:40.38,ASS,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.86,1:47:49.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.53,1:47:54.72,ASS,,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.07,1:48:01.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,快把眼睛睁开
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.94,1:48:10.54,ASS,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.68,1:48:13.41,ASS,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.95,1:48:19.08,ASS,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.23,1:48:27.22,ASS,,0,0,0,,好疼呢
