Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.10,1:48:31.50,ASS,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.51,1:48:38.70,ASS,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.98,1:48:45.91,ASS,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.52,1:48:51.25,ASS,,0,0,0,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.67,1:49:12.07,ASS,,0,0,0,,这是调教
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.28,1:49:16.34,ASS,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:16.34,1:49:18.87,ASS,,0,0,0,,这是调教
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.42,1:49:23.68,ASS,,0,0,0,,怎么了 要回去了吗
