Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.33,1:51:21.80,ASS,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.84,1:51:55.89,ASS,,0,0,0,,来转过去
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.91,1:52:01.77,ASS,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.32,1:52:14.85,ASS,,0,0,0,,快点来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.33,1:52:21.66,ASS,,0,0,0,,来吧
